{"id":3107,"date":"2012-04-28T12:54:01","date_gmt":"2012-04-28T16:54:01","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/www.dailyhadithonline.com\/?p=3107"},"modified":"2019-05-21T16:10:28","modified_gmt":"2019-05-21T12:10:28","slug":"akhirah-laugh-less-weep-more","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/04\/28\/akhirah-laugh-less-weep-more\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Hereafter: If you could see, you will cry more and laugh little"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, led us in prayer on day. The Prophet turned to us and he said, \u201c<strong>O people, I am your leader. Do not precede me in bowing, prostration, standing, and turning. I see you in front of me and behind me<\/strong>.\u201d Then the Prophet said, \u201c<strong>By him in whose hand is the soul of Muhammad, if you could see what I see then you would laugh less and weep more<\/strong>.\u201d They said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what do you see?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201c<strong>I see Paradise and Hellfire<\/strong>.\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 426<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <em><strong>Sahih<\/strong> <\/em>(authentic) according to Muslim<\/p>\n<p align=\"right\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u00a0 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0628\u0650\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0645\u064e \u0630\u064e\u0627\u062a\u064e \u064a\u064e\u0648\u0652\u0645\u064d \u0641\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u0627 \u0642\u064e\u0636\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0635\u064e\u0651\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0642\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0644\u064e \u0639\u064e\u06